# Dashboard Design Template
## Visual Layout & Formatting Guide

---

## Overall Sheet Layout

```
Row 1-3:   HEADER SECTION
           [Title, Subtitle, Last Updated]

Row 5-9:   KPI CARDS SECTION
           [7 major KPIs] [Asset Type KPIs] [% and Trend metrics]

Row 10-17: STATUS BREAKDOWN SECTION
           [Intake status summary table]

Row 18-40: EXCEPTION MONITORING SECTION
           [Missing Docs & Follow-Up table]

Row 42-62: HUMAN REVIEW QUEUE SECTION
           [Priority review items table]

Row 64-72: ASSET TYPE BREAKDOWN SECTION
           [Count and percentage by asset type]

Row 74-94: RECENT LEADS SECTION
           [Last 30 days snapshot]

Columns L-S (on the side or below): CHARTS AREA
```

---

## Color Palette

Use a professional, muted color scheme:

| Element | Color | Hex Code | Usage |
|---------|-------|----------|-------|
| Primary Header | Navy Blue | #1a3a5f | Title row background |
| Section Headers | Medium Gray | #d3d3d3 | Section dividers |
| KPI Background | Light Blue | #e8f1f8 | KPI card backgrounds |
| Table Header | Light Gray | #f0f0f0 | Table header rows |
| Alternating Rows | Very Light Gray | #f9f9f9 | Every other data row |
| Warning/Missing Docs | Amber | #ffd966 | Conditional format flag |
| Critical/Human Review | Light Red | #f4cccc | Conditional format flag |
| Text (Primary) | Dark Gray | #2d2d2d | Standard text |
| Text (Secondary) | Medium Gray | #555555 | Labels, subtitles |
| Border | Light Gray | #cccccc | Table borders |

